{"tid":780160,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港股挫400點  支那小米集團-W跌至16.32穿招股價","createTime":"2018-08-15T03:22:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-15T03:41:44.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"14145c59a05b16438955ed42d4e77dc5aebdb727","tid":780160,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T03:22:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.etnet.com.hk/www/tc/common/chart_oneminute.php?code=1810\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.etnet.com.hk%2Fwww%2Ftc%2Fcommon%2Fchart_oneminute.php%3Fcode%3D1810&h=ce955346&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《經濟通通訊社１５日專訊》小米集團（０１８１０）現價下跌４﹒７８％，報１６﹒３４<br />\n元，失守招股價１７元，並較招股價低３﹒８８％；成交約２１９２萬股，涉資３﹒６４億元。<br />\n<br />\n　　投行Ｂｅｒｎｓｔｅｉｎ指出，不少分析師對小米擴大國際智慧手機市場佔有率期望過高，<br />\n並太過看好通過服務業務提高收入的能力。該行預計小米２０１９年每股盈利較普遍預期低<br />\n２７％，其智慧手機銷售及網際網路服務是推動收益成長的最重要動力。該行予小米「與大市同<br />\n步」評級，目標價１７﹒５元。<br />\n<br />\n　　現時，恆生指數報２７４３６，下跌３１６點或下跌１﹒１４％，主板成交１７０﹒６３億<br />\n元。上證綜合指數報２７６１，下跌１９點或下跌０﹒７０％，成交２１１﹒００億元人民幣。"},{"pid":"19a9e958aabc4d7610647eaec7f31640d0ebf133","tid":780160,"uid":24853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T03:24:13.000Z","msg":"繼續跌"},{"pid":"61b03fab1752d1375c20d16c7d4a79de56fc20ea","tid":780160,"uid":24853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T03:24:25.000Z","msg":"往死裏跌"},{"pid":"85dcc9b4e224b186dd1358df9dc15e39ebe46c2b","tid":780160,"uid":18251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T03:25:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75fa2fef9b18006b91ca7e7a59a0973c767c990d","tid":780160,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T03:27:38.000Z","msg":"佢錢都收晒, 債轉股成功, 最好跌到0都關人撚事, 最好跌到變仙股又私有化, 再上市 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"090c02bde9a93449a1fe70a20c1c81024a390c8d","tid":780160,"uid":116054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T03:28:51.000Z","msg":"老千股"},{"pid":"81bf9425137aac48fe5d1efe8dc0977ee24bfeb5","tid":780160,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T03:35:07.000Z","msg":"跌到私有化美國再上巿囉"},{"pid":"0734f81529ef93b75fa505bb2721af8df6e6f2f4","tid":780160,"uid":7057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T03:41:44.000Z","msg":"中國人的同股不同權的低能股，不了"}]}